OL,11,FJames Trodd, 30, of no fixed address,
OL,12,Ftransferred tens of thousands of
OL,13,Fpounds from victims' bank accounts
OL,14,Fbetween September 2022 and August last
OL,15,Fyear, when he was arrested.
